      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nHello Andreas,\n\n    Not noticing you have investigated this issue.\nI am trying to debug it because it make e2fsprogs test fail today.\n\nI am wondering if some following patch could fix the issue\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20492/\n\nBecause i think we should not really hit ENOCP for this test, since\nthere are still many space left, please suggest.\n\nThank you!\nShilong",
